    "body": "## Fixes\r\nFixes #5685\r\n\r\n## Approach\r\nSupersedes / Obsoletes #10035 and #5686\r\n\r\n- Remove navigation drawer night mode toggle\r\n- Add a `Theme` option where the user can choose the app theme\r\n    - If `Follow system` is selected, app theme will use what is set on `Day` or `Night` theme, depending on user current system mode\r\n    - If any other theme is selected, it will be the app theme and `Day` and `Night` will be disabled\r\n- In API < 29, which don't have a system dark mode option, hide the follow system and day/night modes\r\n\r\nNote: `theme_light`, `theme_plain`, `theme_black`, `theme_dark` need to be moved from their arrays. \r\nThis PR is blocked until then. For now, these strings are being duplicated, as settled in Discord.\r\n\r\n## How Has This Been Tested?\r\n\r\n### API \u2265 29 \r\nOn my device, Samsung Galaxy Note 10 Lite SM-N770F/DS, API 30\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/69634269/158073806-3ed5e6ee-b97e-4f74-a3fc-d2514b7ecf68.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### API < 29\r\nAndroid Studio Emulator, API 25\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/69634269/158073593-46f95126-47e4-4b5a-8162-c1df4eafb0fb.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n## Learning (optional, can help others)\r\nWhen trying to figure out the framents flow:\r\nhttps://developer.android.com/guide/fragments/fragmentmanager\r\nhttps://developer.android.com/reference/androidx/core/app/TaskStackBuilder (not used, handles activities)\r\n\r\nEnums increase the app size\r\nhttps://developer.android.com/topic/performance/reduce-apk-size#remove-enums\r\n\r\n## Strings\r\n![Screenshot_20220313-152749_AnkiDroid](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/69634269/158073847-834ac718-79c7-4c06-a169-de7815918068.png)\r\n![Screenshot_20220313-152806_AnkiDroid](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/69634269/158073850-89423dcf-fc56-403e-a369-d14a25bea69d.png)\r\n\r\n## Checklist\r\n_Please, go through these checks before submitting the PR._\r\n\r\n- [X] You have not changed